_sText: Just a quick Christmas map I made for the GG community, I really like lego maps so I thought why not create one! Has Custom Textures by BoHaRoX, and the green lego texture was by me. Custom Skybox. Get fraggin with the holiday Spirit! Update! Aligned the textures better. Added the FPSB Christmas Logo Moved to the Christmas Contest Section. Added a playerclip Brush around the edge to stop people leaving the map. Better Optimization. Added .nav file
